page.title: 04BUILDINGS
page.content: There are many different buildings in Carlisle. Some are just ordinary houses, and others are of historical interest. Carlisle is a city because we have a cathedral which is very old. It is about 700 years old, and is built of sandstone. We also have a castle which now has a museum. There is also another museum called {Tullie House}. There are also different types of houses such as Victorian and Edwardian. In Carlisle there are a lot of old factories. {Carr's}biscuit factory is an example. It is now owned by United Biscuits.
